{"tid":1386951,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發）北上所見所聞有感！！！香港死撚硬！！！！包括埋警察！！！","createTime":"2019-07-30T12:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:04:58.000Z","uid":206547,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"666abbf0f30ffd5ed40f7102abd536de6b5b4bb5","tid":1386951,"uid":206547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:26:41.000Z","msg":"一出關轉入大陸關口   基本上後生一定檢查手機  話撚知你著乜衫  mk定毒撚   30歲下必查<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關口天花基本上五步十個攝影機  七百二十度零死角烏英都走唔甩！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n深圳多左巡警   基本上一有人聚集就趕   唔理咩人！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唸基本上香港今次真係玩撚完   等今次事件完左之後中共一定即刻做野   到時仲一定唔會俾機會香港出到聲！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到時執法既我唸唔會再用香港警察   終之所有係香港既人都仆硬街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家好至為知   我出完呢個post應該都活唔到幾耐   大家再見了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3c2fa35701494489ea525ea3f3462ec4e375ce","tid":1386951,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:27:51.000Z","msg":"真？"},{"pid":"6992ebb7aac8e1094875955a4517e1365db75fbb","tid":1386951,"uid":99885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:28:33.000Z","msg":"又上去叫雞？"},{"pid":"67aa21081ac32937c614423a251ce01e0489d2e3","tid":1386951,"uid":103759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:44:52.000Z","msg":"麵仔返大陸叫g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chi